{"tid":647900,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"李知恩（IU）笑容有多治愈！網友感慨：她的眼睛裡有星辰大海！","createTime":"2018-04-30T08:41:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T15:31:12.000Z","uid":34643,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"47d65b0f6243b64684b583224fc0a2c4f89c647d","tid":647900,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T08:41:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://t11.baidu.com/it/u=3140899942,2917948581&amp;fm=175&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=640&amp;h=360&amp;s=F2B0446E6C72001D110025A803009013\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3140899942%2C2917948581%26fm%3D175%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D640%26h%3D360%26s%3DF2B0446E6C72001D110025A803009013&h=2e8e3135&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n年僅24歲的李知恩，就已經出道了10年左右了，到仿佛從以前到現在她一直都是全盛時期！古靈精怪、伶俐可愛的她被稱為&ldquo;國民妹妹&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://t10.baidu.com/it/u=3283220541,1037850409&amp;fm=175&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=640&amp;h=360&amp;s=D98189570821C91DE80031ED03007010\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3283220541%2C1037850409%26fm%3D175%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D640%26h%3D360%26s%3DD98189570821C91DE80031ED03007010&h=48e77f03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n演員、MC、歌手，IU這個名字，就像颶風一樣，席卷了演藝界的各個領域、各大榜單。知名度高得嚇人，就連中國的都多地方，都有好多人喜歡她，為她應援。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://t12.baidu.com/it/u=4117401071,2658941410&amp;fm=175&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=640&amp;h=360&amp;s=F2B0446EE4F200350B04B5A803008003\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D4117401071%2C2658941410%26fm%3D175%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D640%26h%3D360%26s%3DF2B0446EE4F200350B04B5A803008003&h=51943b40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為一位歌手，她有著公認的好實力，目前作為演員的iu也有很努力！人美歌甜李知恩，喜歡這樣的女孩子！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://t12.baidu.com/it/u=340218575,116176479&amp;fm=175&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=640&amp;h=360&amp;s=F2B0446E5CF0041D190020A803005013\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D340218575%2C116176479%26fm%3D175%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D640%26h%3D360%26s%3DF2B0446E5CF0041D190020A803005013&h=d57f9a3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n她身上一直少女感，治愈感和清新感，10年來無人可取代！她可能沒有美的驚心動魄，到她的笑卻能感染到我，網友感慨：她的眼睛裡有星辰大海<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://t12.baidu.com/it/u=1408171535,267941711&amp;fm=175&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=640&amp;h=360&amp;s=F2B0446EE4B0103D110121B80300C013\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D1408171535%2C267941711%26fm%3D175%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D640%26h%3D360%26s%3DF2B0446EE4B0103D110121B80300C013&h=8b3d6039&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從08年出道，今年，也正好是IU在這條路上的第十年。這期間，跌跌撞撞、起起落落，圈裡的小忙內，也長成了受人尊敬的大前輩，但算起來，現在的IU，也不過二十五歲而已。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://t12.baidu.com/it/u=319310399,1861823852&amp;fm=175&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=640&amp;h=360&amp;s=72B24C6E6CF2001D1B2020B80300D013\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D319310399%2C1861823852%26fm%3D175%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D640%26h%3D360%26s%3D72B24C6E6CF2001D1B2020B80300D013&h=4cec255e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\niu有種獨特的氣質美，雖說第一眼談不上有多麼抓眼多麼奪目，但這種魅力就好像一杯清茶一樣，越品越有味道。"},{"pid":"3bb84ffe6a748d64b294bfe5bf35888391124f64","tid":647900,"uid":19072,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T08:49:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4943112cf31419db513c3a088bf1adfb2a2947f","tid":647900,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T13:56:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b27b4498e81333eefef6d0d065aa6acbd53b56a8","tid":647900,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bb84ffe6a748d64b294bfe5bf35888391124f64","tid":647900,"uid":19072,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201